British nationals who wish to leave Slovenia are advised to contact their travel operator to make arrangements to do so as soon as possible. Scheduled flights to and from Slovenia have been suspended until at least 30 March.
We are in close touch with the Slovene Government and travel operators and will advise as soon as we have further information.
Further information
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
